 report‚Üê{x}CreateNoticeFile y;list;pkg;name;filename;F;parms;NOTICE;license;else;replace
‚çù Creates NOTICE.md with license information for all Tatin packages found in `from`
‚çù as immediate sub-folders.
‚çù For every package it contains:\\
‚çù * The full name of the package, including the version number
‚çù * The name of the license
‚çù * The license text\\
‚çù As right argument one of these must be provided:
‚çù * A namespace with two variables: "from" and "to".
‚çù * A nested two-element vector with the "from" path and the "to" path.\\
‚çù Optional left argument must be one of:
‚çù * Boolean: 0 = append to existing NOTICE.md if present; 1 (default) = create fresh
‚çù * Vector of text vectors: written to NOTICE.md
‚çù That results in licenses being added to an already existing document.
‚çù Returns '' if all packages had a LICENSE file, otherwise a vector of text vectors with offending package names.
 report‚ÜêNOTICE‚Üê''
 x‚Üê{0<‚éïNC ‚çµ:‚çé‚çµ ‚ãÑ 1}'x'
