     'Invalid left argumemt'Assert‚àß/{' '=‚äÉ1‚Üë0‚ç¥‚çµ}¬®x
     NOTICE‚Üêx
 :EndIf
 F‚Üê##.FilesAndDirs
 :If 9=‚éïNC'y'
     parms‚Üêy
 :Else
     parms‚Üê‚éïNS''
     parms.(from to)‚Üêy
 :EndIf
 'Parameter is missing'Assert 2=+/0<parms.‚éïNC‚Üë'from' 'to'
 :If F.IsDir parms.from
