 :AndIf 0<‚â¢list
     filename‚Üêparms.to,'/NOTICE.md'
     :If F.IsFile filename
         :If replace
             {}F.DeleteFile filename
         :Else
             NOTICE,‚Üê(‚äÉ‚éïNGET filename 1),‚äÇ''
         :EndIf
     :Else
         :If 0=‚â¢NOTICE
             NOTICE‚Üê'# Third-Party Licenses' ''
         :EndIf
     :EndIf
     :For pkg :In list
     ‚çù Immediate sub-folders might be packages
         :If F.IsFile pkg,'/apl-package.json'
             name‚Üê‚äÉ,/1‚Üì‚éïNPARTS pkg
             :If F.IsFile pkg,'/LICENSE'
                 license‚Üê‚äÉ‚éïNGET(pkg,'/LICENSE')1
